#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Why is Tails installing Thunderbird as additional software?\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Pourquoi Tails installe-t-il Thunderbird en tant que logiciel supplémentaire ?\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Since Tails 7.5 (February 2026), Tails tries to automatically install "
"*Thunderbird* as [[additional software|persistent_storage/"
"additional_software]] to improve its security."
msgstr ""
"Depuis Tails 7.5 (février 2026), Tails tente d'installer automatiquement "
"*Thunderbird* en tant que [[logiciel supplémentaire|persistent_storage/"
"additional_software]] pour améliorer sa sécurité."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A new version of *Thunderbird* is released in Debian shortly after each "
"Tails release, because both *Tails* and *Thunderbird* follow the [[release "
"calendar of *Firefox*|https://whattrainisitnow.com/calendar/]]. As a "
"consequence, until Tails 7.5 (February 2026), the version of *Thunderbird* "
"in Tails was almost always outdated, with known security vulnerabilities."
msgstr ""
"Une nouvelle version de *Thunderbird* est publiée dans Debian juste après "
"chaque nouvelle version de Tails, du fait que *Tails* et *Thunderbird* "
"suivent le [[calendrier de *Firefox*|https://whattrainisitnow.com/calendar/]]"
". En conséquence, jusqu'à la version 7.5 de Tails (février 2026), la version "
"de *Thunderbird* dans Tails était presque toujours obsolète, avec des "
"failles de sécurité connues."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"By installing *Thunderbird* as additional software, the latest version of "
"*Thunderbird* is installed automatically from your Persistent Storage each "
"time you start Tails."
msgstr ""
"En installant *Thunderbird* comme logiciel supplémentaire, la dernière "
"version de *Thunderbird* est installée automatiquement depuis le stockage "
"persistant à chaque fois que vous démarrez Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails also tries to install as additional software the language package that "
"corresponds to the language of your first session with Tails 7.5 or later. "
"To use *Thunderbird* in another language, see how to [[use *Thunderbird* in "
"another language|thunderbird#language]]."
msgstr ""
"Tails essaie également d'installer comme logiciel supplémentaire le paquet "
"qui correspond à la langue à votre première session avec Tails 7.5 ou "
"suivant. Pour utiliser *Thunderbird* dans une autre langue, regardez comment "
"[[utiliser *Thunderbird* dans une autre langue|thunderbird#language]]."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*Thunderbird* will no longer be included by default in Tails 7.8 (May 2026)\n"
"and later.\n"
msgstr ""
"*Thunderbird* ne sera plus inclus par défaut dans Tails 7.8 (mai 2026)\n"
"et les versions suivantes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc startlevel=2]]\n"
msgstr "[[!toc startlevel=2]]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Successful migration"
msgstr "Migration réussie"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If the **Thunderbird Migration** dialog below appears when you start "
"*Thunderbird*, it means that Tails successfully installed *Thunderbird* as "
"additional software."
msgstr ""
"Si la fenêtre **Thunderbird Migration** ci-dessous apparaît lorsque vous "
"démarrez *Thunderbird*, cela signifie que Tails a réussi à installer "
"*Thunderbird* en tant que logiciel supplémentaire."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img success.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: Tails installed Thunderbird as additional software to improve its security.\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img success.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: Tails installed Thunderbird as additional software to improve its security.\"]]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Manual migration"
msgstr "Migration manuelle"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If the **Thunderbird Migration** notification below appears when you start "
"Tails, it means that Tails failed to install *Thunderbird* as additional "
"software because the [[Additional Software|persistent_storage/"
"additional_software]] feature of your Persistent Storage is turned off."
msgstr ""
"Si la notification **Thunderbird Migration** ci-dessous apparaît lorsque "
"vous démarrez Tails, cela signifie que Tails n'a pas pu installer "
"*Thunderbird* en tant que logiciel supplémentaire car la fonctionnalité "
"[[Logiciels supplémentaires|persistent_storage/additional_software]] du "
"stockage persistant n'est pas activée."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Select **Install as Additional Software** next time you start Tails to turn "
"on the Additional Software feature of your Persistent Storage and add "
"*Thunderbird* to your list of additional software."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez **Install as Additional Software** la prochaine fois que vous "
"démarrez Tails pour activer la fonctionnalité Logiciels supplémentaires de "
"votre stockage persistant et pour ajouter *Thunderbird* à votre liste de "
"logiciels supplémentaires."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img manual.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: You should install Thunderbird as additional software.\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img manual.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: You should install Thunderbird as additional software.\"]]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Failed migration"
msgstr "Échec de la migration"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If the **Thunderbird Migration** notification below appears when you start "
"Tails, it means that Tails failed to install *Thunderbird* as additional "
"software for unknown reasons."
msgstr ""
"Si la notification **Thunderbird Migration** ci-dessous apparaît lorsque "
"vous démarrez Tails, cela signifie que Tails n'est pas arrivé à installer "
"*Thunderbird* comme logiciel supplémentaire pour des raisons inconnues."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Please [[report an error|first_steps/whisperback]] to help us troubleshoot "
"your problem."
msgstr ""
"Veuillez [[signaler une erreur|first_steps/whisperback]] pour nous aider à "
"résoudre votre problème."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img failure.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: Tails failed to install Thunderbird as additional software.\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img failure.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Thunderbird Migration: Tails failed to install Thunderbird as additional software.\"]]\n"
